examples.en: When he writes for money he knows how to speak intelligibly enough.
examples.ru: Когда он пишет ради денег, он умеет излагать свои мысли вполне четко.

examples.en: The foreigner spoke to us quite intelligibly.

examples.en: Very little of the recording was intelligible.
